5#ifndef V8_EXECUTION_EXECUTION_H_
6#define V8_EXECUTION_EXECUTION_H_
7
8#include "src/common/globals.h"
9
10namespace v8 {
11namespace internal {
12
13class MicrotaskQueue;
14
15class Execution final : public AllStatic {
16 public:
17 // Whether to report pending messages, or keep them pending on the isolate.
18 enum class MessageHandling { kReport, kKeepPending };
19 enum class Target { kCallable, kRunMicrotasks };
20
21 // Call a function (that is not a script), the caller supplies a receiver and
22 // an array of arguments.
23 // When the function called is not in strict mode, receiver is
24 // converted to an object.
25 V8_EXPORT_PRIVATE V8_WARN_UNUSED_RESULT static MaybeHandle<Object> Call(
26 Isolate* isolate, Handle<Object> callable, Handle<Object> receiver,
27 int argc, Handle<Object> argv[]);
28 // Run a script. For JSFunctions that are not scripts, use Execution::Call.
29 // Depending on the script, the host_defined_options might not be used but the
30 // caller has to provide it at all times.
31 V8_EXPORT_PRIVATE V8_WARN_UNUSED_RESULT static MaybeHandle<Object> CallScript(
32 Isolate* isolate, Handle<JSFunction> callable, Handle<Object> receiver,
33 Handle<Object> host_defined_options);
34
35 V8_WARN_UNUSED_RESULT static MaybeHandle<Object> CallBuiltin(
36 Isolate* isolate, Handle<JSFunction> builtin, Handle<Object> receiver,
37 int argc, Handle<Object> argv[]);
38
39 // Construct object from function, the caller supplies an array of
40 // arguments.
41 V8_WARN_UNUSED_RESULT static MaybeHandle<Object> New(
42 Isolate* isolate, Handle<Object> constructor, int argc,
43 Handle<Object> argv[]);
44 V8_WARN_UNUSED_RESULT static MaybeHandle<Object> New(
45 Isolate* isolate, Handle<Object> constructor, Handle<Object> new_target,
46 int argc, Handle<Object> argv[]);
47
48 // Call a function, just like Call(), but handle don't report exceptions
49 // externally.
50 // The return value is either the result of calling the function (if no
51 // exception occurred), or an empty handle.
52 // If message_handling is MessageHandling::kReport, exceptions (except for
53 // termination exceptions) will be stored in exception_out (if not a
54 // nullptr).
55 V8_EXPORT_PRIVATE static MaybeHandle<Object> TryCall(
56 Isolate* isolate, Handle<Object> callable, Handle<Object> receiver,
57 int argc, Handle<Object> argv[], MessageHandling message_handling,
58 MaybeHandle<Object>* exception_out);
59 // Same as Execute::TryCall but for scripts which need an explicit
60 // host-defined options object. See Execution:CallScript
61 V8_EXPORT_PRIVATE static MaybeHandle<Object> TryCallScript(
62 Isolate* isolate, Handle<JSFunction> script_function,
63 Handle<Object> receiver, Handle<FixedArray> host_defined_options);
64
65 // Convenience method for performing RunMicrotasks
66 static MaybeHandle<Object> TryRunMicrotasks(Isolate* isolate,
67 MicrotaskQueue* microtask_queue);
68
69#if V8_ENABLE_WEBASSEMBLY
70 // Call a Wasm function identified by {wasm_call_target} through the
71 // provided {wrapper_code}, which must match the function's signature.
72 // Upon return, either isolate->has_exception() is true, or
73 // the function's return values are in {packed_args}.
74 V8_EXPORT_PRIVATE static void CallWasm(Isolate* isolate,
75 Handle<Code> wrapper_code,
76 Address wasm_call_target,
77 Handle<Object> object_ref,
78 Address packed_args);
79#endif // V8_ENABLE_WEBASSEMBLY
80};
81
82} // namespace internal
83} // namespace v8
84
85#endif // V8_EXECUTION_EXECUTION_H_
